    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "Its museum showcases a vast collection of artifacts and photographs that chronicle East Islip’s evolution from farm to suburb.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        12
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://museumsdatabase.com/museums/view/20856"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The society rescued the Long Island Railroad lean‑to at Great River station, keeping a piece of early rail history intact.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        2
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.gothamcenter.org/long-island-archives1/eastislip-historical-society"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "After a 1995 fire, the society guided the redesign and rebuild of Brookwood Hall Gatehouse, restoring a historic landmark.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
